verses.text:
And them that worship the host of heaven upon the housetops;
and them that worship \add and\add* that swear by the \nd LORD\nd*,
and that swear by Malcham;\f + \fr 1.5  \ft by the…: or, to the \+nd LORD\+nd*\f*

I said, Surely thou wilt fear me, thou wilt receive instruction;
so their dwelling should not be cut off, howsoever I punished them:
but they rose early, \add and\add* corrupted all their doings.

The remnant of Israel shall not do iniquity, nor speak lies;
neither shall a deceitful tongue be found in their mouth: for they shall
feed and lie down, and none shall make \add them\add* afraid.
